{"word":"συλλογιστέος","slug":"συλλογιστέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συλλογιστέος</b></el> <el>(συλλογιστέος, η, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:συλλογίζομαι'><el>συλλογίζομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be concluded</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <el>συλλογιστέον</el> one <i>must compute</i> or <i>conclude</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}